"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-three-storylines-watch-beach-volleyball-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The world's best beach volleyball players will clash again this summer at the2024 Olympic Gamesin Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 103, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999631655, \"rank\": 3.6817037250433464e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the most exciting events in the Summer Olympics will be played at the stadium with arguably the most breathtaking view of any venue in Paris.\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999631655, \"rank\": 3.6817037250433464e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The beach volleyball tournament will be played at Eiffel Tower Stadium, an outdoor venue located right in front of the famous landmark it's named after.\", \"from\": 255, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"J-15 \\u00e2\\u008f\\u00b3Nous \\u00c3\\u00a9tions au site de beach volley et le sable y est !On compte les grains avant le grand jour \\u00e2\\u009c\\u00a8#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/JsqoMySBJP  Fortunately, there are storylines in the sport worthy of such a site.\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 624, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 441, \"end\": 453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"beach volley\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are three big narratives to keep an eye on during the exciting beach volleyball Olympic tournament:  A former NBA player will be fighting for gold at the Eiffel Tower Stadium in Paris.\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.108748495244554e-17, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 808, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999631655, \"rank\": 3.6817037250433464e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Budinger, a formerArizonastar and NBA veteran, beganchasing his Olympic volleyball dreamsafter retiring from professional basketball in 2017.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.108748495244554e-17, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He will become the first athlete in history to play both an NBA regular season game and Olympic beach volleyball.\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1018, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.108748495244554e-17, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over seven NBA seasons, Budinger, a small forward, played for four teams\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094theHouston Rockets,Minnesota Timberwolves,Indiana PacersandPhoenix Suns\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and averaged 7.9 points and three rebounds per game.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.108748495244554e-17, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1167, \"end\": 1176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.8369035601168003, \"rank\": 0.1948654544523888, \"text\": \"Minnesota\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Golden_Gophers_men's_basketball\"}, {\"begin\": 1177, \"end\": 1189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Timberwolves\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7891186263758127e-18, \"text\": \"Timberwolves\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Timberwolves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minnesota_Timberwolves\"}, {\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Hoosiers_men's_basketball\", \"score\": 0.8922831952395509, \"rank\": 0.12072042193450329, \"text\": \"Indiana\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Hoosiers_men's_basketball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indiana_Hoosiers_men's_basketball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But volleyball is not something Budinger just tried out after his basketball career was done.\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Budinger won three volleyball state championships in high school and was named the Mizuno National Player of the Year byVolleyball Magazinein 2006.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He played beach volleyball with friends as part of his cross-training routine during his NBA days and officially made the switch from the hardwood to the sand in 2018.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.108748495244554e-17, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Budinger paired up with five different partners in beach volleyball before landing with Miles Evans in 2023.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1781, \"end\": 1786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9881028089402762, \"rank\": 0.012040434259663642, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, they claimed the second and final U.S. Olympic beach volleyball spot for the Paris Games last month.\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1853, \"end\": 1869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.651524258351736e-24, \"text\": \"beach volleyball\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beach_volleyball\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Budinger and Evans were ranked fourth in the United States last fall.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1921, \"end\": 1926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9881028089402762, \"rank\": 0.012040434259663642, \"te