k\": 3.691718062648631e-12, \"text\": \"Lisboa\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisbon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lisbon\"}, {\"begin\": 3030, \"end\": 3036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999992011438288, \"rank\": 7.967809911784995e-07, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They missed the podium in Tokyo while playing with different partners but are teaming up again after winning gold together at the Youth Olympic Games in 2014 and first place at the 2022 beach volleyball world championships.\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3107, \"end\": 3112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999803128749397, \"rank\": 1.9687510101359586e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There has not been an American duo on the podium in men's beach volleyball since Phil Dalhausser and Todd Rogers in 2008.\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3328, \"end\": 3336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9904003793691379, \"rank\": 0.009652132087313291, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3387, \"end\": 3402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Dalhausser\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phil Dalhausser\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q15117302\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phil_Dalhaus